{"tid":698980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 行管會追游梁186萬薪津 申轉高院審理案件","createTime":"2018-06-12T06:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T10:37:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b28b443b181178da7a199bad84c8408738674e1","tid":698980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"青年新政游蕙禎及梁頌恆被法庭裁定喪失立法會議員資格後，立法會行政管理委員會(行管會)向兩人追討合共186萬港元薪津，惟兩人一直堅拒「回水」，行管會去年正式入稟區域法院追討兩人欠款。案件今(12日)於區院聆案官席前提訊，<span style=\"color: red;\">游梁兩人皆缺席聆訊</span>。原告律師指因本案申索金額超越區院的司法管轄權，故申請將案件轉往高院審理。原告並指至今未收到2名被告確認得悉有關訴訟的通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bkn-20180612133807630-0612_00822_001.html?view=d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180612%2Fbkn-20180612133807630-0612_00822_001.html%3Fview%3Dd&d=X8zxGnOiSvha2XF4qVEAMttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9c3fbab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180612/bkn-20180612133807630-0612_00822_001.html?view=d</a>"},{"pid":"0a37206af5a330b2b4e14292739968bf8521865c","tid":698980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"游b如何出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bc1639e88b0dad20ae106742a80e9f3edfef59","tid":698980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/145512_a31112fa7d1d7718a78bc6e3c7c30b19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F145512_a31112fa7d1d7718a78bc6e3c7c30b19.png&h=4ea8d6e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb7b6ae6272d8703434008ce3e715493b3c1b921","tid":698980,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a37206af5a330b2b4e14292739968bf8521865c","tid":698980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:54:00.0